  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasDataPoints, HasDataset, HasFill

    public final class ScatterDataset
extends LineDataset
    The scatter chart allows a number of properties to be specified for each dataset. These are used to set display properties for a specific dataset.
    Extends the line dataset to set fixed properties for scatter chart.
    The scatter dataset can use ONLY data points. If you try to use array of data numbers, an exception will be thrown.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
